{"tid":539922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[你講我寫]gothic calligraphy","createTime":"2018-01-25T04:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T04:25:51.000Z","uid":73362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55c24afc8cf4aefeaa48da19ce5addf53ca222a6","tid":539922,"uid":73362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:08:06.000Z","msg":"新手上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想練吓字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zjy21auq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzjy21auq&h=9a4b67e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b52a57a37396cf4997e577421afe7e8d6c2febbe","tid":539922,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:09:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09595a399128ac3becf02d685087cd6cbf33afe5","tid":539922,"uid":73362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I spent my life in foreign lands. So many men have tried to kill me, I don't remember all their names. I have been sold like a broodmare. I've been chained and betrayed, raped and defiled. Do you know what kept me standing through all those years in exile? Faith. Not in any gods. Not in myths and legends. In myself. In Daenerys Targaryen. The world hadn't seen a dragon in centuries until my children were born. The Dothraki hadn't crossed the sea. Any sea. They did for me. I was born to rule the Seven Kingdoms, and I will.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9da0f0d0eedd3944fe78967ea44ca07959dcef","tid":539922,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"Erika Ikuta"},{"pid":"cb360f18f8f2ddec347f4331677172e183312e7b","tid":539922,"uid":73362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"<b